item.title: 【Albums (lossy)】PACK - 4minute Discography (iTunes Plus + Melon Mp3 320kbps)
item.description:
4minute (포미닛; also stylized as 4Minute and 4MINUTE) was a five-member girl group formed by Cube Entertainment in 2009. They released their debut single "Hot Issue" on June 15, 2009 and made their debut stage June 18, 2009 on Mnet's M! Countdown.
On June 15, 2016, Cube announced the group's disbandment after the members (with the exception of HyunA) decided not to renew their contracts with the agency.
